OL,3,CFamily of Mabli Cariad Hall win award
OL,4,Cfor courage
OL,6,FMabli Hall was just eight months old
OL,7,Fwhen she died after being struck by a
OL,8,Fcar outside a hospital.
OL,10,FBridget Curtis, 71, who was driving
OL,11,Fthe vehicle that hit Mabli outside
OL,12,FWithybush Hospital in Haverfordwest,
OL,13,Fpleaded guilty to causing death by
OL,14,Fdangerous driving last September and
OL,15,Fwas sentenced to four years in prison,
OL,16,Flater reduced to three.
OL,18,FEver since, parents Gwen and Rob Hall
OL,19,Fhave raised more than #30,000 for
OL,20,Fcharities such as 2wish, while also
OL,21,Fcoming to terms with their own grief.
