OL,3,CFamily of Mabli Cariad Hall win award
OL,4,Cfor courage
OL,6,FTomorrow evening, the Hall family will
OL,7,Fbe recognised as the Courageous Family
OL,8,Fof the Year at the Child of Wales
OL,9,FAwards in Swansea, in light of their
OL,10,Fstrength, unity and compassion
OL,11,Ffollowing an unimaginable loss.
OL,13,FIn an exclusive interview with ITV
OL,14,FWales, the family shared their
OL,15,Fexperience of life since Mabli's death.
