OL,3,CFamily of Mabli Cariad Hall win award
OL,4,Cfor courage
OL,6,FMabli had been visiting the hospital
OL,7,Fwith her family to see her paternal
OL,8,Fgrandmother Betty Hall, who was there
OL,9,Freceiving end-of-life care, when she
OL,10,Fhit by a car just outside of the
OL,11,Fhospital and later died of her
OL,12,Finjuries.
OL,14,FCurtis, who was driving, had turned to
OL,15,Fretrieve a handbag when she lost
OL,16,Fcontrol of the vehicle and accelerated
OL,17,Fforwards and collided with Mabli's
OL,18,Fpram.
OL,20,FA day later, Rob's mother, Betty, died.
