OL,3,CFamily of Mabli Cariad Hall win award
OL,4,Cfor courage
OL,6,FReflecting on that time, Rob said:
OL,7,F"One of the things I said to my wife
OL,8,Fand to all of the family that were in
OL,9,Fthere is: 'We will keep Mabli's name
OL,10,Fgoing'.
OL,12,F"We will do everything we can just to
OL,13,Fhave her name out there, her picture
OL,14,Fout there. We will do whatever it
OL,15,Ftakes because that's all we can do.
OL,17,F"The amount of support we have had
OL,18,Ffrom friends and family who have done
OL,19,Ffundraisers for us is incredible. And
OL,20,Fthe amount of money that we have
OL,21,Fraised so far is just amazing."
