OL,3,CFamily of Mabli Cariad Hall win award
OL,4,Cfor courage
OL,6,FGwen added: "We are just so grateful
OL,7,Fthat people want to do good in Mabli's
OL,8,Fname, and that's really important to
OL,9,Fus - that her name does good. It means
OL,10,Fthe world to us as a family."
OL,12,FIt was on the second anniversary of
OL,13,FMabli's passing, when the family heard
OL,14,Fthey were nominated by 2wish for an
OL,15,Faward and had won.
OL,17,F"We just couldn't believe it, that on
OL,18,Fthat day of all days we were nominated
OL,19,Ffor an award," Gwen said. "For us it
OL,20,Fwas like a sign from Mabli."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/9
