OL,3,CFamily of Mabli Cariad Hall win award
OL,4,Cfor courage
OL,6,FRob added: "With the term 'won' or
OL,7,F'win' it is quite hard to navigate
OL,8,Fthat when you have lost your child.
OL,10,F"But, when you look at it and this
OL,11,Famazing awards ceremony that happens,
OL,12,Fand when you actually sit down and
OL,13,Fthink about the amazing things we've
OL,14,Fdone, and the kids have done, the
OL,15,Ffamily and the support, it is
OL,16,Fincredible and it does make sense."
