OL,3,CFamily of Mabli Cariad Hall win award
OL,4,Cfor courage
OL,6,FOn their children, Rob said: "Our kids
OL,7,Fare just incredible, and for us, the
OL,8,F'courageous-ness' is theirs. They are
OL,9,Funbelievable for everything that they
OL,10,Fhave been through, and still continue
OL,11,Fto go through.
OL,13,F"The girls they struggle everyday.
OL,14,FAnd, trying to manage kids that age,
OL,15,Fand getting them to school and things
OL,16,Flike that, is difficult. But we
OL,17,Fcouldn't be prouder of all five them.
OL,18,FAnd they help us as well - they lift
OL,19,Fus. It's a privilege to see them
OL,20,Fcontinue."
