OL,3,CFamily of Mabli Cariad Hall win award
OL,4,Cfor courage
OL,6,FGwen added: "We know now that growing
OL,7,Fup is a privilege. Growing old is a
OL,8,Fprivilege. And to see the children
OL,9,Fgrow and be the amazing people that
OL,10,Fthey are, we are just grateful for
OL,11,Fthat because we have experienced the
OL,12,Fultimate loss."
OL,14,FThe Child of Wales Awards in Swansea
OL,15,Fare to be held on Friday, 12
OL,16,FSeptember, at Swansea Arena.
OL,18,FLooking ahead to the event, Rob said:
OL,19,F"Mabli is going to be there with us.
OL,20,FHer pictures will be up there. Her
OL,21,Fvideos will be up there.
