OL,3,CFamily of Mabli Cariad Hall win award
OL,4,Cfor courage
OL,6,F"We are already looking now to next
OL,7,Fyear, at what we can do, to raise
OL,8,Fmoney for her. This is the only way
OL,9,Fcan have our daughter."
OL,11,FGwen added: "It's all for Mabli.
OL,12,FThat's the reason we are doing this."
